---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import GoplcNav from '../../components/GoplcNav.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="GOPLC Features" description="Deep dive into GOPLC's capabilities: web IDE, AI code generation, boss/minion clustering, 14+ protocol drivers, step debugger, Node-RED integration, and more.">
  <GoplcNav />

  <!-- Header -->
  <section class="bg-gray-950 text-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <div class="inline-block bg-accent/10 text-accent px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6 border border-accent/20">
          Features
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6">
          Every Feature.<br />
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00ADD8] to-[#4ec9b0]">Every Detail.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          GOPLC isn't a proof of concept. It's 180,000+ lines of production-grade Go code with capabilities that don't exist anywhere else in industrial automation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Web IDE -->
  <section id="ide" class="py-24 scroll-mt-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="inline-block bg-[#00ADD8]/10 text-[#00ADD8] px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">
            Development
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary-dark mb-6">
            Web-Based IDE with Monaco Editor
          </h2>
          <p class="text-text-light mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            The same editor engine that powers VS Code, running in your browser. Full IEC 61131-3 Structured Text support with syntax highlighting, autocomplete, error detection, code folding, multi-cursor editing, and find-and-replace with regex.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-light mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            No software to install. No licenses to manage. Open a browser, point it at your PLC, and start programming. Works from a tablet on the plant floor or a laptop in the control room.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-text">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
              IEC 61131-3 Structured Text syntax highlighting
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-text">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
              Autocomplete for 1,600+ built-in functions
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-text">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
              Multi-user simultaneous access
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-text">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
              Hot reload &mdash; deploy without stopping the runtime
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl border border-gray-200">
          <img src="/images/showcase/goplc-ide-features.png" alt="GOPLC IDE with Monaco editor showing Structured Text code, syntax highlighting, and code navigation features" class="w-full" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Online Mode -->
  <section id="online" class="py-24 bg-gray-50 scroll-mt-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
          <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl border border-gray-200">
            <img src="/images/showcase/goplc-monitor-variables.png" alt="GOPLC live variable monitoring with real-time inline values, color-coded data types, and WebSocket streaming" class="w-full" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
          <div class="inline-block bg-[#4ec9b0]/10 text-[#4ec9b0] px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">
            Monitoring
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary-dark mb-6">
            Online Mode &mdash; Live Variable Monitoring
          </h2>
          <p class="text-text-light mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Enter online mode and live values appear inline next to every variable declaration and assignment. Color-coded by data type, with expandable arrays and structures.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-light mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Traditional PLCs require expensive vendor software (Studio 5000, TIA Portal) installed on a dedicated workstation. GOPLC streams live values to any browser via WebSocket. Multiple users can monitor simultaneously.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-text">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
              Real-time inline variable values via WebSocket
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-text">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
              Configurable update rate
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-text">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
              Expandable arrays and structured data types
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Step Debugger -->
  <section id="debugger" class="py-24 scroll-mt-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="inline-block bg-[#00ADD8]/10 text-[#00ADD8] px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">
            Debugging
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary-dark mb-6">
            Statement-Level Step Debugger
          </h2>
          <p class="text-text-light mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Traditional PLCs offer limited debugging &mdash; maybe online monitoring of variable values. GOPLC brings modern software debugging to industrial control. Set breakpoints on any line. Step through code statement by statement. Inspect and modify variables in real time. View the full call stack.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-light mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Ten dedicated API endpoints power the debugger, with multi-task awareness so you can debug across concurrent PLC tasks. All running in a standard web browser.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-text">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
              Breakpoints, step into, step over, step out
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-text">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
              Live variable inspection and modification
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-text">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
              Full call stack visualization
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-text">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
              Multi-task awareness across concurrent programs
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <!-- Debugger Visual Panel -->
        <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl border border-gray-800">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 bg-gray-800 border-b border-gray-700">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500"></div>
            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></div>
            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>
            <span class="text-gray-500 text-xs ml-2">GOPLC Debugger &mdash; Main.st</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 font-mono text-sm leading-loose">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-500">
              <span class="w-8 text-right text-xs">12</span>
              <span class="w-3"></span>
              <span class="text-purple-400">VAR</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-500">
              <span class="w-8 text-right text-xs">13</span>
              <span class="w-3"></span>
              <span>  temp : <span class="text-blue-400">REAL</span>;</span>
              <span class="ml-auto text-[#4ec9b0] text-xs">72.4</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-500">
              <span class="w-8 text-right text-xs">14</span>
              <span class="w-3"></span>
              <span>  sp   : <span class="text-blue-400">REAL</span> := <span class="text-green-400">75.0</span>;</span>
              <span class="ml-auto text-[#4ec9b0] text-xs">75.0</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-500">
              <span class="w-8 text-right text-xs">15</span>
              <span class="w-3"></span>
              <span class="text-purple-400">END_VAR</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-500">
              <span class="w-8 text-right text-xs">16</span>
              <span class="w-3"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-yellow-500/10 -mx-6 px-6 border-l-2 border-yellow-500">
              <span class="w-8 text-right text-xs text-yellow-500">17</span>
              <span class="w-3 text-red-500 text-xs font-bold">*</span>
              <span class="text-white">temp := <span class="text-yellow-300">ReadAnalog</span>(<span class="text-green-400">0</span>);</span>
              <span class="ml-auto text-yellow-400 text-xs font-bold">BREAKPOINT</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-500">
              <span class="w-8 text-right text-xs">18</span>
              <span class="w-3"></span>
              <span><span class="text-purple-400">IF</span> temp > sp <span class="text-purple-400">THEN</span></span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-500">
              <span class="w-8 text-right text-xs">19</span>
              <span class="w-3"></span>
              <span>  alarm := <span class="text-blue-400">TRUE</span>;</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-500">
              <span class="w-8 text-right text-xs">20</span>
              <span class="w-3"></span>
              <span class="text-purple-400">END_IF</span>;</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="px-6 py-4 bg-gray-800 border-t border-gray-700 flex items-center gap-3">
            <button class="bg-[#00ADD8] text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded">Step Over</button>
            <button class="bg-gray-700 text-gray-300 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded">Step Into</button>
            <button class="bg-gray-700 text-gray-300 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded">Step Out</button>
            <button class="bg-green-600 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded ml-auto">Continue</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AI Code Generation -->
  <section id="ai" class="py-24 bg-gray-50 scroll-mt-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <!-- AI Visual Panel -->
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
          <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl border border-gray-800">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 bg-gray-800 border-b border-gray-700">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500"></div>
              <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></div>
              <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>
              <span class="text-gray-500 text-xs ml-2">AI Assistant</span>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <!-- User prompt -->
              <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
                <div class="text-gray-500 text-xs mb-2">You</div>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">"Write a PID loop that reads analog input 0, maintains 75 degrees, and triggers an alarm above 95"</p>
              </div>
              <!-- AI response -->
              <div class="mb-4">
                <div class="text-[#4ec9b0] text-xs mb-2">GOPLC AI &mdash; Claude</div>
                <div class="text-green-400 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed">
                  <pre class="overflow-x-auto"><code>PROGRAM TempControl
VAR
  sensor : REAL;
  output : REAL;
  alarm  : BOOL;
  pid    : PID_CONTROLLER;
END_VAR

sensor := ReadAnalog(0);
output := PID(
  pv := sensor,
  sp := 75.0,
  kp := 1.2,
  ki := 0.05,
  kd := 0.3
);
WriteAnalog(0, output);
alarm := sensor > 95.0;</code></pre>
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- Status bar -->
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-xs text-gray-500 pt-4 border-t border-gray-800">
                <span class="text-green-400 flex items-center gap-1">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
                  Compiled successfully
                </span>
                <span>6 functions used</span>
                <span>All functions valid</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
          <div class="inline-block bg-[#4ec9b0]/10 text-[#4ec9b0] px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">
            Artificial Intelligence
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary-dark mb-6">
            AI-Powered Code Generation &amp; Agentic Control
          </h2>
          <p class="text-text-light mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Describe what you want in plain English. GOPLC's AI generates working Structured Text code using the full registry of 1,600+ built-in functions &mdash; not generic code that references functions that don't exist, but code that actually compiles and runs.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-light mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Beyond code generation, GOPLC features an <strong>agentic control loop</strong> where AI operates the PLC directly through 12 built-in tools &mdash; reading sensors, writing setpoints, deploying programs, and managing tasks in autonomous multi-turn conversations.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-6 mb-6">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-primary-dark mb-3 text-sm">Supported AI Providers</h4>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center text-sm">
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-primary-dark">Claude</div>
                <div class="text-text-light text-xs">Best for complex logic</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-primary-dark">OpenAI</div>
                <div class="text-text-light text-xs">Strong general-purpose</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-primary-dark">Ollama</div>
                <div class="text-text-light text-xs">Local / air-gapped</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-text">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
              AI generates ST code, HMI pages, and Node-RED flows
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-text">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
              12 built-in AI tools for autonomous operation
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-text">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
              Ollama support for fully air-gapped environments
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Boss/Minion Clustering -->
  <section id="clustering" class="py-24 scroll-mt-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="inline-block bg-[#00ADD8]/10 text-[#00ADD8] px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">
            Architecture
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary-dark mb-6">
            Boss/Minion Clustering
          </h2>
          <p class="text-text-light mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Traditional PLCs are islands. Each one is an isolated controller with no concept of distributed coordination. GOPLC breaks this paradigm with its Boss/Minion architecture &mdash; a central Boss coordinates thousands of Minion instances, each executing control logic independently.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-light mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Tested at scale with 10,000+ concurrent PLC instances and 620,000+ aggregate scans per second. Linear scaling to 500 minions at 95%+ efficiency. Nested proxy support for hierarchical deployments across multiple sites.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-white mb-4 text-sm">Benchmark Results (31 cores)</h4>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span class="text-gray-400">Throughput improvement</span>
                <span class="text-accent font-bold">10.4x</span>
              </div>
              <div class="border-t border-gray-700"></div>
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span class="text-gray-400">Aggregate scans/sec</span>
                <span class="text-[#00ADD8] font-bold">620,949</span>
              </div>
              <div class="border-t border-gray-700"></div>
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span class="text-gray-400">DataLayer latency (avg)</span>
                <span class="text-[#4ec9b0] font-bold">1.7 &micro;s</span>
              </div>
              <div class="border-t border-gray-700"></div>
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span class="text-gray-400">DataLayer latency (p99)</span>
                <span class="text-[#4ec9b0] font-bold">8.2 &micro;s</span>
              </div>
              <div class="border-t border-gray-700"></div>
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span class="text-gray-400">Docker container overhead</span>
                <span class="text-green-400 font-bold">ZERO</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Clustering Architecture Visual -->
        <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl border border-gray-800 p-8">
          <!-- Boss -->
          <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent/20 text-accent font-bold px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-accent/30">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 12h14M5 12a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2M5 12a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2" /></svg>
              BOSS
            </div>
            <div class="text-gray-500 text-xs mt-2">Coordinator &bull; Web IDE &bull; Fleet Management</div>
          </div>
          <!-- Connection lines -->
          <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
            <div class="w-px h-6 bg-gray-700"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
            <div class="h-px w-3/4 bg-gray-700"></div>
          </div>
          <!-- Minions Row 1 -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-2 mb-3">
            <div class="bg-[#00ADD8]/10 border border-[#00ADD8]/30 rounded-lg p-3 text-center">
